ygData.messageBody:
It takes you to NK.  To get to SK, run south from druid ring, then turn right once you hit the water.  Follow the water on your right to the bridge by the wizzie spires, take the bridge to SK.  Run all the way south through SK to find the aviak city, good exp there for you at 20th.
 
----- Original Message -----
From: Legleiter
Sent: Saturday, June 16, 2001 3:20 PM
To: EverQuest@yahoogroups.com
Subject: [EverQuest] lvl 20?
 
I'm a lvl 20 Druid where can I get good exp? is SK any good? I don't want to go to loio. I need some help. And I need to know dose the lvl 19 druid ring spell port me to EK or NK? I was thinking is was NK but I don't know.
